{{zh-hanzi|[[三]][[令]][[五]][[申]]}}
==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: sān lìng wŭ shēn
===[[Min Nan]]===
[[POJ]]: sam-lēng-ngó•-sin

===Etymology===
Literally: Give three orders and five explanations.

===Idiom===
# To repeatedly [[admonish]].
# To repeatedly [[warn]].
#: ''[[尽管]][[你]]'''三令五申'''，[[有]][[许多]][[员工]][[就是]][[不]][[肯]][[照办]].'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])
#: ''[[儘管]][[你]]'''三令五申'''，[[有]][[許多]][[員工]][[就是]][[不]][[肯]][[照辦]].'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])
#: ''No matter how much you '''warn and admonish''' them, there are many employees who just aren't willing to do as they are told.''

